text: Vintage Cellars is an Australian liquor chain owned by Wesfarmers and is positioned at the higher end of the market compared with the Liquorland and 1st Choice Liquor Superstore, Wesfarmers' other liquor brands. The chain comprised 83 stores as at June 2018. ==References== Category:1951 establishments in Australia Category:Retail companies established in 1951 Category:Alcohol distribution retailers in Australia Category:Coles Group
